  "levels": {
    "B2": {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo lived in a small apartment in the city.",
              "audioStart": 0.1,
              "audioEnd": 2.263
            },
            {
              "text": "Every morning, he followed the same routine before he walked to work.",
              "audioStart": 3.125,
              "audioEnd": 6.775
            },
            {
              "text": "He would drink coffee, eat a piece of bread, and check his pockets for the blue house key.",
              "audioStart": 7.638,
              "audioEnd": 12.3
            },
            {
              "text": "Today, the morning seemed normal, but Leo felt a little distracted.",
              "audioStart": 13.162,
              "audioEnd": 17.087
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "When he reached his office, Leo realized the key was not in his bag.",
              "audioStart": 17.95,
              "audioEnd": 21.7
            },
            {
              "text": "If he had been more careful, he would not have lost it.",
              "audioStart": 22.562,
              "audioEnd": 25.462
            },
            {
              "text": "The key, which was important for his home, had probably fallen out during his walk.",
              "audioStart": 26.325,
              "audioEnd": 30.812
            },
            {
              "text": "He decided to return to the park immediately.",
              "audioStart": 31.675,
              "audioEnd": 34
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "The park was quiet and the sun began to go down.",
              "audioStart": 34.862,
              "audioEnd": 37.55
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo walked slowly along the path where he had been earlier.",
              "audioStart": 38.413,
              "audioEnd": 41.462
            },
            {
              "text": "He looked under every tree and around every bush.",
              "audioStart": 42.325,
              "audioEnd": 44.925
            },
            {
              "text": "The situation was difficult because the light was fading fast.",
              "audioStart": 45.788,
              "audioEnd": 49.125
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "He remembered that he had stopped to watch some birds near a wooden bench.",
              "audioStart": 49.987,
              "audioEnd": 53.388
            },
            {
              "text": "Perhaps the key had fallen while he sat there to rest.",
              "audioStart": 54.25,
              "audioEnd": 56.962
            },
            {
              "text": "He walked toward the bench and looked down at the ground.",
              "audioStart": 57.825,
              "audioEnd": 60.325
            },
            {
              "text": "The grass was long and thick, making it hard to see anything small.",
              "audioStart": 61.188,
              "audioEnd": 64.812
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Finally, Leo reached the bench and knelt on the cold ground.",
              "audioStart": 65.675,
              "audioEnd": 68.8
            },
            {
              "text": "He checked under the wooden structure and moved some dry leaves aside.",
              "audioStart": 69.662,
              "audioEnd": 72.912
            },
            {
              "text": "There it was, the blue key, shining faintly in the dark.",
              "audioStart": 73.775,
              "audioEnd": 77.125
            },
            {
              "text": "He picked it up with a smile and felt a great sense of relief.",
              "audioStart": 77.987,
              "audioEnd": 81.112
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "His day had been stressful, but the problem was solved.",
              "audioStart": 81.975,
              "audioEnd": 84.938
            },
            {
              "text": "He walked back home, glad that he had retraced his steps.",
              "audioStart": 85.8,
              "audioEnd": 88.987
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo understood that he should be more careful in the future.",
              "audioStart": 89.85,
              "audioEnd": 92.725
            },
            {
              "text": "He arrived at his house just as the night became completely dark.",
              "audioStart": 93.588,
              "audioEnd": 97.013
            }
          ]
        }
